      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been maintained to an exacting standard. This is an investment-grade example, offering the refined performance and aesthetic integrity one expects from a showroom-quality acquisition. We invite serious collectors to inspect a machine that truly transcends the typical pre-owned market.",
