    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garage-kept and making sure it stayed spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better. If you're looking for something that's been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
