      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a dream! This car has been seriously babied and kept in absolutely flawless shape. It honestly feels like it just rolled off the lot. If you want that new-car feeling without the new-car price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one. It\u2019s spotless inside and out and ready for a new home!",
